# Employee Attrition Prediction using Machine Learning

## 📌 Project Overview
This project predicts employee attrition using Machine Learning techniques on the IBM HR Analytics Employee Attrition & Performance dataset. The goal is to identify employees who are likely to leave the organization and provide HR with actionable insights to improve employee retention.

---

## 📂 Dataset
**Dataset Name:** IBM HR Analytics Employee Attrition & Performance

The dataset contains **1,470 employee records** with **35 features**, including employee demographics, job information, salary, work experience, job satisfaction, overtime, work-life balance, and performance-related attributes.

**Target Variable:**
- **Attrition**
  - Yes = Employee Left
  - No = Employee Stayed

